Configuration
**************

Configuration File Locations
=============================

Session configuration files are stored in these locations:

  1. ./etc/kitty/                (project-local sessions)
  2. ~/.local/etc/kitty/         (user sessions, created by --create)
  3. /opt/etc/kitty/             (system-wide sessions)
  4. ~/.config/kitty/            (kitty standard location)


Session File Format
===================

Session files use the kitty session configuration format. Basic example:

   # Define the first tab
   new_tab Main
     cd /path/to/project
     launch

   # Define the second tab
   new_tab Development
     launch


For complete documentation, see:
https://sw.kovidgoyal.net/kitty/conf/


